{
  "stem": "16245.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 279.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't honestly remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to Australia illegally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no legal way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nobody to give you a passport, and nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to Vienna illegally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did I get there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember how I got to the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just walked across the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was only Russians to worry about borders then, and they didn't particularly worry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I got a local train to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stayed at first with friends of my father's who knew them from way back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was in the American zone and I got papers after a while.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on I managed to get myself a Hungarian passport, so for a while I could go back in school holidays.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I perceived less anti-Semitism in Vienna than in Budapest, but I was probably wrong.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You see what you want to see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was also more familiar with Budapest, so I saw more of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And certainly at the University, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] if-- for instance, the professors were all old men, either men who retired before the Nazis took over or Jews who came back from overseas.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the students were all veterans, most of them older than I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were usually men in their-- from 25 to 30 who really wanted to get on with their lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were probably in a prison camp or in the army or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most of them were years older than I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Vienna itself was bombed to ribbons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't much to look at in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Food was very scarce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was starvation for years after.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
